- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of CAD drawings for programming and simulation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as the paper may discuss the use of computer vision in the robot-assisted sheet metal bending cell. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper may discuss the control systems used in the robot-assisted sheet metal bending cell.
